Package: data.trame
Type: Package
Version: 0.9.0
Title: A better 'data.frame' for 'SciViews::R'
Description: The 'data.trame' object is an hybrid between 'data.table',
  'tibble' and 'data.frame'. It enhances the 'data.frame' with the speed of
  'data.table' and the nice features of 'tibble' (petty printing, stricter
  rules...).
